                            <comment id="15136307" author="lehmi" created="Sun, 7 Feb 2016 16:39:12 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The CIDFontType2 isn&apos;t a true type font as expected but an open type font and the fallback font doesn&apos;t work&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15136311" author="jira-bot" created="Sun, 7 Feb 2016 16:41:18 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Commit 1728988 from &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=lehmi&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;lehmi&quot;&gt;lehmi&lt;/a&gt; in branch &apos;pdfbox/trunk&apos;&lt;br/&gt;
[ &lt;a href=&quot;https://svn.apache.org/r1728988&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://svn.apache.org/r1728988&lt;/a&gt; ]&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-2957&quot; title=&quot;Glyphs rendered as gibberish&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PDFBOX-2957&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PDFBOX-2957&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: omit the CID2GID mapping if the embedded font is replaced by an external font&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15136314" author="lehmi" created="Sun, 7 Feb 2016 16:45:31 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The fallback font didn&apos;t work due to the CID2GID mapping. My change omits the mapping if the embedded font is replaced so that the rendering works now.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
